Description
===========

This is a very simple but raw and limited irc serveur in python.

Why SIRCD?
==========

It was intended as part of a SMS phone application as an IPC with computers.

Documentation
=============

Usage: sircd.py [PORT]

Option:
    PORT        Port on which the server will listen. Default is 6667

Dependencies
============

docopt  https://github.com/docopt/docopt or "pip install docopt"

